Common.tti_selectCountry:
To enable FoS capability the following criteria must be met:-

  • if the producing country is non FoS, then you only need to choose at least 1 FoS country.

  • if the producing country is FoS then you must choose at least 1 FoS country and 1 non FoS country OR at least 2 FoS countries
Common.tti_selectFosCountry:
To be a valid FoS program the following criteria must be met:-

  • At least 1 FoS country must be selected from the selected Countries.

  • If the producing country is FoS then you must have at least one local (Non-FoS) country.
Common.tti_selectCountryNew:
To be a valid MNP program the following criteria must be met:-

  • For a Non FoS program, at least 1 local country must be selected that is not the same as the producing country.

  • For a FoS program, if the producing country is FoS then at least 1 local country must be selected that is not the same as the producing country.
Common.tti_selectFosCountryNew:
To be a valid MNP FoS program the following criteria must be met:-

  • For a Master Issuing FoS program, at least 1 local FoS country must be selected that is not the same as the producing/issuing country.

  • For a Issuing FoS program at least 1 FoS country must be selected.
